description.en: WARRIOR is dedicated to advancing the global film and television media industry through the use of blockchain technology as its core foundation. With a comprehensive approach, we aim to leverage the unique capabilities of blockchain to transform various aspects of the industry, including content creation, distribution, financing, and protection of intellectual property.
